<% 
def getDate(datetime) 
    return datetime[0, 10]
end

def getTime(datetime) 
    return datetime[11, 8]
end
%>

<p><%= @user.inspect %> </p>
<div class=" page" id = "cover"   >
   
      <h1> Coding report for <%= @username %> </h1>
      <h1><%= @username %></h1>
      <p>Welcome to <%= @username %>'s page</p>
      <img src = '<%= @image %>'>
  <button class="btn btn-info btn-lg next">Next <i class="fa fa-angle-double-down" aria-hidden="true"></i> </button>
</div>
<div class=" page hide">
   <button class="btn btn-info btn-lg back">Back <i class="fa fa-angle-double-up" aria-hidden="true"></i> </button>
       <!--<h1> you have the 1 page</h1>-->
       <p> Hello, <span> <%= @user.login %> </span>!  </p>
       <p> You created your GitHub account at <span> <%= getDate(@user.createat) %> </span> </p>
       <p>Is it a long journey?</p>
       <p>Remember your first piece of code (survived) ?</p>
       <p> It's <span> <%= @user.old_repo %></span>, you created it at <span> <%= getDate(@user.old_repo_time) %> </span>
       </p>
       <div>
          <img width = 500px height = 300px src = 'https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/modules/open_graph/github-octocat.png'>
       </div>
   <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg next">Next <i class="fa fa-angle-double-down" aria-hidden="true"></i> </button>
</div>
<div class="page hide">
  
   <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg back">Back <i class="fa fa-angle-double-up" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
   <!--<h1> you have the 2 page</h1>-->
   <p> Of course you have met some coding buddies, you like watching <span> <%= @user.following %> </span> guys' codes. </p>
   <p>There are also <span> <%= @user.followers %> </span> hackers thinking your code is cute.</p>
   <% if(@user.followers < "5") then  %>
   <p> Congratulation! </p>
   <% else %>
   <p> Come on! Make more friends.</p>
   <% end %>
   <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg next">Next <i class="fa fa-angle-double-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
</div>
<div class="page hide">
   <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg back">Back <i class="fa fa-angle-double-up" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
   <!--<h1> you have the 3 page</h1>//TODO-->
   <p>Among your <span> <%= @user.public_repos  %> </span> repositories,</p>
   <p>
      your best mate is <span> <%= @user.lang1  %> </span> 
   </p>
   <p>
      you have  created  <span> <%= @user.lang1num  %> </span> repositor<%= if @user.lang1num.to_i <= 1 then 'y' else 'ies' end %> by this language. 
   </p>
   <% if @user.lang2 %>
   <p>Followed by <span><%= @user.lang2 %></span>: <span><%= @user.lang2num %></span>
   <% end %>
   <% if @user.lang3 %>
   ; <span><%= @user.lang3 %></span>: <span><%= @user.lang3num %></span>
   <% end %>
   <% if @user.lang2 %>
   </p>
   <% end %>
   <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg next">Next <i class="fa fa-angle-double-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
</div>
<div class="page hide">
   <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg back">Back <i class="fa fa-angle-double-up" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
   <!--<h1> you have the 4 page</h1>//TODO-->
   <p> 
   Until now, <span> <%= @user.commits_num  %> </span> commits have been produced by you to the world,
   </p>
   <p> 
   The largest project you have been working on is <span> <%= @user.big_repo %> </span> with <span> <%= @user.big_repo_commits_num %> </span> commits. </span> 
   </p>
   <p>
       <% if @user.big_repo_commits_num > "50" %>
           Great job!
        <% else %>
            Actually, it's not that large..
        <% end %>
   </p>
   <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg next">Next <i class="fa fa-angle-double-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
</div>
<div class="page hide">
   <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg back">Back <i class="fa fa-angle-double-up" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
   <!--<h1> you have the 5 page</h1>//TODO-->
   <p> <span> <%= getDate(@user.most_commits_time) %> </span></p>
   <p>literaly, is your big day (or bug day?), </p>
   <p>you proposed <span> <%= @user.most_commits_num  %> </span> commits on that day.</p>
   <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg next">Next <i class="fa fa-angle-double-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
</div>
<div class="page hide" >
   <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg back">Back <i class="fa fa-angle-double-up" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
  
    <p>
        On <span> <%= getDate(@user.late_commit_time)  %> </span>,
    </p>
   <p>
      You slept so late.
   </p>
   <p>
      Kept coding until <span><%= getTime(@user.late_commit_time) %></span>
   </p>
   <p>
       At that moment, project <span> <%= @user.late_commit_repo  %> </span> was with you.
   </p>
</div>
    
<script>
  $('.next').click(function(){
  $(this).parent().toggleClass('hide').next().toggleClass('hide');
});

$('.back').click(function(){
   $(this).parent().toggleClass('hide').prev().toggleClass('hide');
});

$('.back').html('<i class="fa fa-angle-double-up" aria-hidden="true"></i>');
$('.next').html('<i class="fa fa-angle-double-down" aria-hidden="true"></i>');
</script>   
